data.description: Welcome to this BEAUTIFUL two bedroom two bath condo located on the fourth floor. Upon entering, you'll be greeted by an open and inviting living and dining area, perfect for entertaining guests or simply relaxing after a long day. The primary bedroom offers a spacious layout with plenty of natural light. The second bedroom is also generously sized with its own bathroom just across the hall. This condo boasts stunning views of the surrounding cityscape and abundant natural light throughout. Other highlights include in-unit laundry and a private balcony located on the West side of the building for stunning Mountain views. Perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or evening cocktail. Residents of this building can enjoy a large updated fitness center, Sauna, pool table and so much more! With a prime location near the heart of downtown, you'll have easy access to top-rated restaurants, shopping, and plenty of entertainment options. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful condo your new home! Schedule a showing today! It's truly a MUST SEE !!
